Program to calculate the maximum credits of accounts.

Read account number.
Read balance at the beginning of the month.
Read total of all items charged by the customer this month.
Read total of all credits applied to the customer's account this month.
Read allowed credit limit.

while account number is greater than zero
	display the new balance.
	if the account exceeded the limit credit
		display "Credit limit exceeded".

	Read account number.
	Read balance at the beginning of the month.
	Read total of all items charged by the customer this month.
	Read total of all credits applied to the customer's account this month.
	Read allowed credit limit.


